ecific task.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13.3333px;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13.3333px;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Though I live in the area, I am not capable of doing anything personally. However, if anybody in troubles like this is interested and visits me, I can give some\n ash from my daily homam of divine Mother. They can apply it on the forehead of the person everyday. Of course, I don&#39;t know if it will help in any way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13.3333px;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13.3333px;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;If interested, please send a private email to pvr108@....&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13.3333px;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;Best regards,&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality\n Resources: &lt;a rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;&gt;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt